2026-03-28T06:28:38.6657236Z               "message": "Scope fallback to EmailAddressRejectionException only\n\nReplace broad Exception catch with a custom EmailAddressRejectionException\ntype so transient network errors and cancellations propagate directly\nwithout triggering individual-send fallback.\n\n- EmailAddressRejectionException added to Hpoll.Core.Exceptions\n- SesEmailSender wraps MessageRejectedException as\n  EmailAddressRejectionException; all other exceptions pass through\n- EmailSchedulerService catches only EmailAddressRejectionException for\n  fallback (OperationCanceledException guard no longer needed)\n- SesEmailSenderTests updated: MessageRejectedException wrapped, other\n  exceptions propagate, new network-error test\n- EmailSchedulerServiceTests: fallback tests use\n  EmailAddressRejectionException, new test confirms network errors do\n  not trigger fallback\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01GYPAPQwDpWkpzVSP1ync2h",
